<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>It was recently reported she had relocated to Beverly Hills with her beau.</p>

<p>Yet Dua Lipa appeared to be back in New York on Monday, as she and boyfriend Anwar Hadid enjoyed dinner and drinks with a friends in the city.</p>

<p>The singer, 25, seemed to be in great spirits as she dined at Gemma, where she sipped on red wine and laughed and chatted to Anwar and their friend.</p>

<p>Laughing: Dua Lipa appeared to be back in New York on Monday, as she and boyfriend Anwar Hadid enjoyed dinner and drinks with a friends in the city</p>

<p>Dua looked typically stylish at dinner in a flower print cardigan, which she wore over a black crop top and a pair of jeans, teamed with trainers.</p>

<p>She wore her sleek raven locks in a chic up do and highlighted her pretty features with light touches of make-up.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, Anwar, 21, also opted for a casual look as he sported a red and blue checked shirt jacket, which he styled with jeans and black trainers.</p>

<p>At one stage in the night, the couple were seen sitting on a bench while Anwar stopped to roll a cigarette. </p>

<p>Taking a break: At one stage in the night, the couple were seen sitting on a bench while Anwar stopped to roll a cigarette</p>

<p>Hanging out: The singer, 25, seemed to be in great spirits as she dined at Gemma, where she sipped on red wine and laughed and chatted to Anwar and their friend</p>

<p>Fashion: Dua looked typically stylish at dinner in a flower print cardigan, which she wore over a black crop top and a pair of jeans, teamed with trainers.</p>

<p>It was reported last week that Dua has upped sticks and travelled across the pond to Los Angeles to be closer to California native Anwar.</p>

<p>The Sun reported The One Kiss hitmaker has relocated stateside to live with her partner due to fears that she won't be able to travel to and fro because of the novel coronavirus pandemic.</p>

<p>It was claimed the London-born artist has moved into a lavish property in Beverly Hills near to Anwar's family, despite the fact that her inner circle are all based in the UK.</p>

<p>Glam: She wore her sleek raven locks in a chic up do and highlighted her pretty features with light touches of make-up</p>

<p>Relaxed: Meanwhile, Anwar, 21, also opted for a casual look as he sported a red and blue checked shirt jacket, which he styled with jeans and black trainers</p>

<p>Stateside: It was reported last week that Dua has upped sticks and travelled across the pond to Los Angeles to be closer to California native Anwar</p>

<p>A source told the publication: 'It was difficult to get to the US in the first place and she knows it's not going to be easy going back and forth because she would have to quarantine for weeks on end.</p>

<p>'But she knows plenty of people in Los Angeles, as does Anwar, who has lived there in the past, so she's feeling optimistic.</p>

<p>'Being in the US right now is great for pushing her career there too, especially with new music coming out. Dua's making their new place nice and homely and she has just got a puppy called Dexter with Anwar because they see their future in LA.'</p>

<p>MailOnline contacted representatives for Dua and Anwar for comment at the time.</p>

